tr.td: Reduced file size. Adjusted aspect ratio to exactly 16:9. Changed nominal dimensions to 1200x675. Moved inuksuk such that its upper peak sits on flag's vertical centerline. Converted the slightly asymmetric star into a perfect regular pentagram. Adjusted position of star so that its center point is exactly 1/5 of the flag's height from both top and right edges of the flag.
